sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User (browser)
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant ING as ingestion
    participant GEN as generation
    participant SEC as secrets
    participant P as provider (selected)
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant EXP as export

    U->>API: Upload CV (PDF/DOCX) or type background
    API->>ING: extract_text(file) / normalize(manual)
    ING-->>API: structured background text
    API->>DB: persist Profile

    U->>API: Submit job + "Generate" (lang, provider)
    API->>DB: persist JobInput
    API->>GEN: generate(profile, job, lang, provider_id)
    GEN->>SEC: get_key(provider_id)
    SEC-->>GEN: decrypted key (if cloud)
    GEN->>GEN: build prompt (sanitize injected text)
    GEN->>P: complete(prompt)
    P-->>GEN: draft letter
    GEN->>DB: persist CoverLetter (v1)
    GEN-->>API: draft
    API-->>U: render in editor (AI-assist mode)

    U->>API: Edit manually / regenerate section
    API->>DB: persist CoverLetter (v2…)

    U->>API: Export (pdf/html/md/txt/docx)
    API->>EXP: render(letter, format)
    EXP-->>API: file bytes
    API-->>U: download
